documentation:
Quick entry is assumed to be a UPC scan or similar user input.  If a
matching product can be found, this will add a new row for the batch;
otherwise an error is raised.

Returns boolean indicating whether the given batch is eligible
for the "auto receive" function,
i.e. {meth}`auto_receive_all_items()`.

